The paper describes a computational simulation of evolving entities with symbiosis, which suggests practical applications in evolutionary computation. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory).
